# ROVEXO v1.0 — LOGIN FINAL FREEZE + AUTH POLICY

**STATUS: APPROVED | CERTIFIED | PRODUCTION READY | FROZEN | PERMANENTLY LOCKED | 100/100**

**Login v1.0 is a READ-ONLY canonical component.** All Cursor agents must obey this policy.

